description: This Chainlink VRF top 5% score Plezier purrs with a rating of 24, and a multiplier of 8x. It has a total score of 192, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Nine Lives for North, 1 for East, 1 for South, and 1 for West. Plezier has the personality suit of yenta. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/70248-91114-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Plezier [192 Votes, Top 5% Score]
